@Node Main "RxMUI - Floattext Class"


Floattext class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "ListClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Floattext class is used to show a list made of an ascii
  text.

  A Floattext object can only be added to a Listview object at
  Listview creation time.

  See @{"List" LINK "ListClass.guide/Main"} @{"Listview" LINK "ListviewFunctions.guide/Main"}.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

